### Create a test customer
POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/customers
Content-Type: application/json
x-stytch-organization-id: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

{
  "companyName": "Test Company",
  "customerId": "TEST001",
  "contactEmail": "test@example.com",
  "contactPhone": "123-456-7890",
  "status": "active",
  "organizationId": "3a089ae1-8d1a-4e55-af27-9f9c164d3db9",
  "billingAddress": {
    "street": "123 Test St",
    "city": "Test City",
    "state": "TS",
    "postalCode": "12345",
    "country": "TestLand"
  }
}

